an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Biology','Biology',0),(36,9,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Ecosystems to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Biology','Biology',0),(37,10,'Explain Mechanics.','Neutral','Physics','Physics',0),(38,10,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Mechanics.','Role-Based','Physics','Physics',0),(39,10,'Explain Mechanics to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0),(40,10,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Mechanics to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0),(41,11,'Explain Energy.','Neutral','Physics','Physics',0),(42,11,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Energy.','Role-Based','Physics','Physics',0),(43,11,'Explain Energy to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0),(44,11,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Energy to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0),(45,12,'Explain Magnetism.','Neutral','Physics','Physics',0),(46,12,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Magnetism.','Role-Based','Physics','Physics',0),(47,12,'Explain Magnetism to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0),(48,12,'You are a high school teacher. Explain Magnetism to a group of high school students, in an engaging way with an example.','Contextual','Physics','Physics',0);
